The paper discusses the publishing behavior of Indonesian academics and their preference for conference proceedings over journal articles. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
